Package Models

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
Models.Appointment
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class Appointment extends Object implements Serializable
The Appointment class represents a medical appointment in the system. It stores details such as the appointment ID, patient ID, doctor ID, appointment time, status, and outcome record. This class implements Serializable for enabling data persistence.
